title: Meta signs commercial AI data agreements with publishers to offer real-time news on Meta AI
description: Meta is partnering with CNN, Fox News, Fox Sports, Le Monde Group, the People Inc. portfolio of media brands, The Daily Caller, The Washington Examiner, and USA Today.
